   DISR NEWS

   WellPoint-CareFirst Submit Merger Plans
   CareFirst, Group Hospitalization and Medical Services (GHMSI) and
   WellPoint Health Networks have filed an application with DISR for
   permission to convert the non-profit GHMSI to for-profit status. Full
   Text

   DISR Encourages District Residents to "Get Smart" About Insurance
   January 14-18, 2002 has been designated "Get Smart Week". When it comes
   to insurance, knowledge is your best policy. Full Text

   Holocaust Survivors Urged to File Unpaid Claims
   Survivors and heirs need to file unpaid Holocaust-era insurance claims
   by the February 15, 2002 deadline. Full Text

   Exclusions Related to Acts of Terrorism
   Limited exclusions for acts of terrorism approved in the District; P&C
   insurers writing commercial lines given procedure to expedite filing
   and timely review. Full Text
